{"tid":728571,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"［貓撚入］一個人住養一隻貓，隻貓算唔算好慘","createTime":"2018-07-04T00:03:27.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-24T15:08:03.000Z","uid":175659,"like":3,"dislike":21,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"6915c8eea1941cfc0f78ed7d50a55627e655196e","tid":728571,"uid":175659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-04T00:03:27.000Z","msg":"朝朝返工隻貓都sense到你將會出門口十幾個鐘，佢會好淒慘咁叫一聲再望實你出門去<br />\n<br />\n夜晚返黎又冇精力陪佢玩，餵完罐搞下自己野就要訓，最多同佢玩一陣<br />\n<br />\n訓緊覺果陣如果佢想撩玩又會罵佢嘈住晒<br />\n<br />\n第二朝又loop<br />\n<br />\n咁樣隻貓係咪好慘"},{"pid":"c55ad2e07e7022a8dfb4421c14c85479a8590f9c","tid":728571,"uid":1082,"like":24,"dislike":2,"score":22,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-04T00:04:17.000Z","msg":"係，搵個伴比佢"},{"pid":"910aa44318b8da95943af7d02e900c81d909f1b2","tid":728571,"uid":175659,"like":1,"dislike":23,"score":-22,"quote":{"pid":"c55ad2e07e7022a8dfb4421c14c85479a8590f9c","tid":728571,"uid":1082,"like":24,"dislike":2,"score":22,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-04T00:04:17.000Z","msg":"係，搵個伴比佢"},"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2018-07-04T00:08:18.000Z","msg":"養一隻已經全屋貓毛飄揚、周地貓沙<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f8f3cca12addf643ee29136eec5cbcfcb4d8aebb","tid":728571,"uid":190181,"like":9,"dislike":2,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-04T00:15:59.000Z","msg":"養隻倉鼠比佢玩"},{"pid":"3cef5f3f0768ee613db479c10e5685fb3ff512fb","tid":728571,"uid":116131,"like":63,"dislike":1,"score":62,"quote":{"pid":"910aa44318b8da95943af7d02e900c81d909f1b2","tid":728571,"uid":175659,"like":1,"dislike":23,"score":-22,"quote":{"pid":"c55ad2e07e7022a8dfb4421c14c85479a8590f9c","tid":728571,"uid":1082,"like":24,"dislike":2,"score":22,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-04T00:04:17.000Z","msg":"係，搵個伴比佢"},"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2018-07-04T00:08:18.000Z","msg":"養一隻已經全屋貓毛飄揚、周地貓沙<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-04T00:25:20.000Z","msg":"反正都已經係成屋貓毛啦，咪養多隻<br />\n<br />\n聽講啲貓寂寞太耐會有個幻想玩伴同佢地玩，所以夜晚有時你會見佢自己一個好high咁跑嚟跑去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申 以前養一隻，見到佢好悶咁決定養多隻<br />\n而家兩隻夜晚會一齊玩，冬天會訓埋一齊取暖，兩隻都好嗲"},{"pid":"fb02d18e97caedf771a03b242d22d17bbb1853fa","tid":728571,"uid":17520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-04T01:02:37.000Z","msg":"你問下佢"},{"pid":"70c5caef1c780d1dba2f24a8554f92840b5c6ee7","tid":728571,"uid":136537,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"quote":{"pid":"910aa44318b8da95943af7d02e900c81d909f1b2","tid":728571,"uid":175659,"like":1,"dislike":23,"score":-22,"quote":{"pid":"c55ad2e07e7022a8dfb4421c14c85479a8590f9c","tid":728571,"uid":1082,"like":24,"dislike":2,"score":22,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-04T00:04:17.000Z","msg":"係，搵個伴比佢"},"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2018-07-04T00:08:18.000Z","msg":"養一隻已經全屋貓毛飄揚、周地貓沙<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-04T01:46:30.000Z","msg":"慘架 其實貓唔係真係咁獨立<br />\n佢都想有人陪同錫<br />\n咁樣佢遲d可能會抑鬱 悶到嘔<br />\n<br />\n反正宜家你屋企咁多毛 都唔差在<br />\n其實你可以同佢梳多d毛<br />\n用隔貓砂既廁所<br />\n希望你會養多隻貓陪下佢啦"},{"pid":"657e68aec63963cd26eac75b1acbd5cf00b41671","tid":728571,"uid":175659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"70c5caef1c780d1dba2f24a8554f92840b5c6ee7","tid":728571,"uid":136537,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"quote":{"pid":"910aa44318b8da95943af7d02e900c81d909f1b2","tid":728571,"uid":175659,"like":1,"dislike":23,"score":-22,"quote":{"pid":"c55ad2e07e7022a8dfb4421c14c85479a8590f9c","tid":728571,"uid":1082,"like":24,"dislike":2,"score":22,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-04T00:04:17.000Z","msg":"係，搵個伴比佢"},"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2018-07-04T00:08:18.000Z","msg":"養一隻已經全屋貓毛飄揚、周地貓沙<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-04T01:46:30.000Z","msg":"慘架 其實貓唔係真係咁獨立<br />\n佢都想有人陪同錫<br />\n咁樣佢遲d可能會抑鬱 悶到嘔<br />\n<br />\n反正宜家你屋企咁多毛 都唔差在<br />\n其實你可以同佢梳多d毛<br />\n用隔貓砂既廁所<br />\n希望你會養多隻貓陪下佢啦"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-04T12:43:47.000Z","msg":"其實我覺得越梳間屋越多毛<br />\n而家通常約人都會約去